PrecisAmendment (SCHEDULE No. 991) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which sets a Maximum Residue Limit on any trace amounts of the insecticide IMIDACLOPRID and its metabolites that can be detected on potatoes (0.3 ppm).
